Dark Sidenav

An alternate option for the sidenav styling
Dark Sidenav Option
Use the .sidenav-dark with the .sidenav for a darker layout for the side navigation element. The text, icons, and all of the elements within the side navigation will adapt to work well with darker backgrounds. You can also use utility classes to modify the background color of the side navigation, or use a custom style!
